			Company Description 


			HCSB Financial Corp. operates as bank holding company, engages in the provision of consumer and business banking services through its subsidiary, Horry County State Bank. It offers deposit products, cash management services, safe deposit boxes, travelers checks, direct deposit of payroll and social ...
		


                HCSB Financial Corp. operates as bank holding company, engages in the provision of consumer and business banking services through its subsidiary, Horry County State Bank. It offers deposit products, cash management services, safe deposit boxes, travelers checks, direct deposit of payroll and social security checks, automatic drafts, and credit card services. The company was founded on June 10, 1999 and is headquartered in Loris, SC.
            




